Ubuntu 8.10 x86 64-bit
  ### TODO: move the ruby installs into chef.
  * rm -rf /root/.gem && touch /root/.gem && chown 000 /root/.gem
  * apt-get update
  * sudo apt-get install ruby ruby1.8-dev rubygems libopenssl-ruby1.8 libsqlite3-ruby build-essential git-core
	
  * gem install rubygems-update
  * sudo /var/lib/gems/1.8/bin/update_rubygems
  * sudo gem install chef ohai --source http://gems.opscode.com --source http://gems.rubyforge.org

  ### Run chef solo.
  * cd /tmp/ && git clone git://github.com/retr0h/chef_solo_web_with_passenger.git
  * cd chef_solo_web_with_passenger
  * sudo chef-solo -l debug -c config/solo.rb -j config/dna.json
